data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. SELLERS ARE OFFERING $5,000 TOWARD CLOSING COSTS/RATE BUY-DOWN WITH ACCEPTED OFFER.  Look no further! Why wait for new construction?  Curb appeal galore in this magnificent home in Waterset.  The home features 1,493 sq. ft., 3 bedroom/2 bathrooms and an attached 2 car garage with paver driveway and walkways. The open and light-filled living area beautifully combines kitchen, dining room and living room and allows for flexibility in furnishings.  Two-way split plan allows for privacy. A cook's kitchen with gas range, quartz countertops, tile backsplash and a large island with plenty of seating.  Ceramic tile in the living areas and carpet in the bedrooms. Laundry room with cabinetry and front south-facing window provides plenty of light to work by.  Master bedroom features a master bathroom with double vanity, large stall shower, beautiful decorative tile and large walk-in closet. Fully fenced backyard and covered lanai allow for outdoor enjoyment.  Nicely landscaped property.  This property is a short walk to and in close proximity to a clubhouse, pool, basketball and tennis courts!  Waterset is an impressive community with charming architecture and numerous amenities including club houses, pools and many other recreational options.  From this home, it's a short distance to all of Tampa Bay's many attractions; Gulf beaches, boating, local shopping, restaurants and Interstate-75. A great commute to points north and south. Make this beautiful home your own!
